  <brief_title>Topical Oestrogens and Antimuscarinics In The Treatment Of Detrusor Overactivity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is There A Synergic Effect Of Topical Oestrogens When Associated To Antimuscarinics In The Treatment Of Symptomatic Detrusor Overactivity</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Università degli Studi dell'Insubria</agency>
